From the past few days, some people have been asking me about how to start contributing to open source. 
So, I've created a thread sharing my learnings on getting started with open source

Name: Anshul Wadhwa
Content: Collaborate and learn: Start engaging with the community members and ask questions related to the project. This way you will learn from experienced contributors and make valuable connections.

Name: Anshul Wadhwa
Content:
That's a wrap.
If you find this thread helpful, don't forget to like and retweet it to share it with others.
